Gii thiu chung

Trong nhng nm gn y, cc nh phn tch v nh u t ngy cng quan tm n vic nh gi ri ro ti chnh trong sn xut phim. Nghin cu ny s dng phn tch hi quy tuyn tnh bi d on thnh cng v mt ti chnh ca phim v nghin cu mi quan h gia s ln chiu v nm.

Kt qu t c

Bng phn cng cng vic

Pht biu bi ton

Mc tiu chnh ca n l khm ph v phn tch tng doanh thu ca phim trong hai nm 2014 v 2015 cng nh kim tra mi quan h v ngha ca mt s bin gii thch. Hn na, n xy dng mt m hnh hi quy ti u a ra d on v s thnh cng v mt ti chnh, tc l tng doanh thu ca mt b phim trong hai nm 2014 v 2015.

Gii thiu v d liu

B d liu phim truyn thng v x hi (conventional and social media dataset) c s dng trong n ny c cu trc tng i n gin m mt s ngi c ch kin thc v phim truyn hnh cng c th hiu c. Vn chnh ca b d liu l missing values, v chng ti s c gng x l n bng mt s k thut bit.

Ngnh cng nghip in nh l mt ngnh ng gp ng k cho nn kinh t ca mt quc gia v l mt nh tuyn dng ln ti Hoa K. Do chi ph ln lin quan n sn xut phim, cc nh phn tch cn nghin cu v hiu cc bin s chnh gp phn vo thnh cng v mt thng mi v ti chnh ca mt b phim. n c th cung cp thng tin chi tit v cc tnh nng chnh gp phn vo thnh cng v mt ti chnh ca cc b phim v thc y nghin cu trong tng lai xem xt mi quan h gia cc bin gii thch c bit c o trong tp d liu. Hn na n cn c th gip cc nh sn xut phim xc nh nhng tnh nng no cn tp trung vo trong giai on qung b ci thin thnh cng ca b phim.

remove_high_vif <- function(regr_variable, data, threshold = 5) {      
    stop <- FALSE
    while(stop == FALSE) {
        # Tnh VIF cho cc bin c lp
        model <- lm(as.formula(paste(regr_variable, "~ .")), data = data)
        vif_values <- vif(model)
        # Tm cc bin c VIF cao hn ngng
        high_vif <- which(vif_values > threshold)
        
        if (length(high_vif) > 0) {
            # Loi b cc bin c VIF cao
            remove_index <- which.max(high_vif)
            rm_names <- names(data[, !names(data) %in% regr_variable])
            rm_name <- rm_names[remove_index]
            data <- data[, !names(data) %in% rm_name]
        } else {
            stop <- TRUE
        }
    }
    return(data)
}

missing_ratio <- function(s) {
  round(mean(is.na(s)) * 100, 1)
}

# Hm tnh ton trung v (median)
median_custom <- function(df) {
  round(quantile(df, 0.5, na.rm = TRUE), 1)
}

# Hm tnh ton phn v 25% (Q1)
lower_quartile <- function(df) {
  round(quantile(df, 0.25, na.rm = TRUE), 1)
}

# Hm tnh ton phn v 75% (Q3)
upper_quartile <- function(df) {
  round(quantile(df, 0.75, na.rm = TRUE), 1)
}

# Tnh ton t l gi tr missing value
missing_ratio <- function(s) {
  round(mean(is.na(s)) * 100, 1)
}

# Function to calculate number of unique values
num_values <- function(s) {
  s <- as.character(s)  # Convert factors to character
  s <- strsplit(s, ";")
  s <- unlist(s)
  length(unique(s))
}

# Hm tnh ton t l cc gi tr ca bin ca phn loi
value_ratios <- function(s) {
  s <- as.character(s)  # Convert factors to character
  s <- strsplit(s, ";")
  s <- unlist(s)
  totalCount <- sum(!is.na(s))
  value_counts <- table(s)
  ratios <- round((value_counts / totalCount) * 100, 1)
  as.list(ratios)
}

# La chn cc ct c kiu phn loi
cat_col_info_df <- processed_data %>%
  select_if(~ is.character(.) || is.factor(.))

# Hm tng hp kt qu cho mi ct
aggregate_results <- function(df) {
  result <- data.frame(
    column = names(df),
    missing_ratio = sapply(df, missing_ratio),
    num_values = sapply(df, num_values),
    value_ratios = I(lapply(df, value_ratios))
  )
  result
}

# p dng hm tng hp kt qu

  • im xp hng cng cao th doanh thu ca mt b phim cng cao (hp l theo logic thng thng).
  • S lt ch cng cao th doanh thu ca mt b phim cng cao. iu ny c th l gii, khi mt b phim c nhiu bnh lun tiu cc, ngi ta s c hng th i xem n bit ti sao n b ch (yu t t m).

Phn tch Residuals vs Fitted Plot

Biu Residuals vs Fitted Plot a ra du hiu nu c cc mu phi tuyn tnh. hi quy tuyn tnh chnh xc, d liu cn phi tuyn tnh nn iu ny s kim tra xem iu kin c c p ng hay khng.

In[]:
plot(best_model_csm, which=1, col=c("blue")) # Residuals vs Fitted Plot

Da trn biu ny, ta thy ng cong mu c dng cha gn nh mt ng thng, v cc phn t tri dc theo ng cong ny mt cch tng cha ng u. iu ny chng t c quan h phi tuyn xut hin trong d liu.

Phn tch Normal QQ (quantile-quantile) Plot

In[]:
plot(best_model_csm, which=2, col=c("blue")) # QQ Plot

Cc gi tr thng d (residual) nn c phn phi chun. kim tra iu ny, chng ta cn quan st biu QQ Residuals plot, nu cc im c xp thnh mt ng thng (hoc gn nh thng) th chng t cc gi tr thng d (residual) c phn phi chun. Nh hnh v kt qu trn, ta thy r iu , residual c phn phi chun.

Cn thn hn, chng ta th dng ShapiroWilk test kim tra c ng tht l cc gi tr thng d c phn phi chun hay khng?

  • H0: Bin thng d ca m hnh phn phi chun trong mt s qun th.
  • H1: Bin thng d ca m hnh khng phn phi chun trong mt s qun th.
In[]:
# Shapiro-Wilk normality test
shapiro.test(residuals(best_model_csm))

	Shapiro-Wilk normality test

data:  residuals(best_model_csm)
W = 0.98029, p-value = 0.0172

Kt qu cho thy p-value b hn mc ngha alpha 0.05 nn ta cha c th bc b gi thhuyt H0, bin thng d ca chng ta chun trong mt s qun th.

Phn tch Scale-Location

Biu scale-location kim nh gi nh hi quy v phng sai bng nhau (homoscedasticity), tc l gi tr thng d c phng sai bng vi ng hi quy.

In[]:
plot(best_model_csm, which=3, col=c("blue")) # Scale-Location

Ta pht hin:

  • ng mu gn b lch v pha di ca biu . Ngha l, phn tn ca gi tr thng d gn khng bng nhau tt c cc gi tr ph hp.
  • Cc gi tr thng d c phn tn ngu nhin xung quanh ng mu vi bin thin khng bng nhau tt c cc gi tr ph hp.

Cn thn hn, chng ta s dng Breusch-Pagan test kim tra c tht l nh vy khng?

  • H0: Cc gi tr thng d l homoscedastic
  • H1: Cc gi tr thng d l heteroscedastic
In[]:

M hnh ha bng PCR

Principal Component Regression (PCR) l mt k thut kt hp Phn tch thnh phn chnh (PCA) v hi quy tuyn tnh gii quyt a cng tuyn v gim chiu trong cc tp d liu cao chiu. Cc bc chnh trong PCR l:

  • Principal Component Analysis (PCA): PCA bin i cc bin d bo ban u thnh mt tp hp cc bin mi, khng tng quan c gi l cc thnh phn chnh. Cc thnh phn ny l cc t hp tuyn tnh ca cc bin ban u v c sp xp theo lng phng sai m chng gii thch trong d liu. Mi thnh phn chnh nm bt c phng sai ti a c th trong khi vn trc giao vi cc thnh phn trc .
  • Regression: Mt tp hp con cc thnh phn chnh (gii thch phng sai ln nht) c chn v s dng lm cc yu t d bo trong m hnh hi quy tuyn tnh d bo bin phn hi. Bng cch tp trung vo cc thnh phn chnh nm bt c phng sai ln nht, PCR hng n mc tiu xy dng mt m hnh hi quy n nh v d din gii hn.

# Hm tin x l d liu vi box-cox
f <- function(df) {
    col.names <- names(df)

    transformed_df <- df
    
    for (name in names(processed_data_final))
    {
        col.name <- name

        # Rt trch bin phn hi
        response_variable <- df[[col.name]]
        
        if (!is.numeric(response_variable)) {
            stop("The column to be transformed must be numeric.")
        }
        
        if (any(response_variable <= 0)) {
            # Shift the values to be positive
            shift_value <- abs(min(response_variable)) + 1
            response_variable <- response_variable + shift_value
        }
        
        # p dng box-cox transform  tm lambda ti u
        boxcox_result <- boxcox(lm(response_variable ~ 1), plotit = FALSE)
        optimal_lambda <- boxcox_result$x[which.max(boxcox_result$y)]
        print(paste("Optimal lambda:", optimal_lambda))
        
        # S dng lambda ti u  bin i d liu
        if (optimal_lambda == 0) {
            transformed_response <- log(response_variable)
        } else {
            transformed_response <- (response_variable^optimal_lambda - 1) / optimal_lambda
        }
        
        # Gn bin  c bin i
        transformed_df[[col.name]] <- transformed_response
    }
    
    return(transformed_df)
}

processed_data <- f(processed_data_final)

i s xc thc = CV ch nh rng xc thc cho (cross-validation - CV) nn c s dng xc thc m hnh. Xc thc cho l mt phng php mnh m nh gi hiu sut d on ca mt m hnh. N bao gm vic phn vng d liu thnh cc tp hp con, hun luyn m hnh trn mt s tp hp con (b hun luyn - training set) v xc thc n trn cc tp hp con cn li (b xc thc - validation set). Qu trnh ny c lp li nhiu ln m bo hiu sut ca m hnh l nht qun v khng ph thuc vo phn vng d liu c th.

Bng cch s dng xc thc cho, m hnh t c kh nng qu khp vi d liu hun luyn. Qu khp xy ra khi m hnh nm bt c nhiu v cc mu c th trong d liu hun luyn khng tng qut ha thnh d liu mi, cha tng thy. Xc thc cho gip pht hin v gim thiu tnh trng qu khp bng cch kim tra m hnh trn cc tp hp con khc nhau ca d liu.
